<section id="types" style="padding-top:0"><div class="wrap">
  <div class="sechead"><div>
    <div class="k">Deal Types</div>
    <h2>Six ways to get funded.</h2>
    <p>Every deal type has a deep-dive guide — what it is, when to use it, and exactly how we fund it. Learn it, then launch it.</p>
  </div><button class="btn" onclick="openModal()">Get Funded ⚡</button></div>
  <div class="types">
    <div class="ty"><div class="ic">◈</div><h3>Morby Method</h3><p>Seller carry + primary lender stacked into one creative close. Often little or no cash to close — sometimes cash back.</p><div class="acts"><button class="learn" onclick="openDrawer('morby')">Learn more</button><button class="start" onclick="openModal('morby')">Start →</button></div></div>
    <div class="ty"><div class="ic">◎</div><h3>Echo Method</h3><p>Buy like a cash buyer with our capital, then repay it with your end loan at a same-day second closing.</p><div class="acts"><button class="learn" onclick="openDrawer('echo')">Learn more</button><button class="start" onclick="openModal('echo')">Start →</button></div></div>
    <div class="ty"><div class="ic">⇄</div><h3>Double Close</h3><p>100% A-to-B funding for back-to-back closings. Your spread stays private and your name stays on the contract.</p><div class="acts"><button class="learn" onclick="openDrawer('dc')">Learn more</button><button class="start" onclick="openModal('dc')">Start →</button></div></div>
    <div class="ty"><div class="ic">🔒</div><h3>EMD</h3><p>Earnest money wired before your deadline. Never lose a contract waiting on capital.</p><div class="acts"><button class="learn" onclick="openDrawer('emd')">Learn more</button><button class="start" onclick="openModal('emd')">Start →</button></div></div>
    <div class="ty"><div class="ic">⚒</div><h3>Hard Money</h3><p>Asset-based loans for flips and value-add projects, underwritten on the deal — not your W-2.</p><div class="acts"><button class="learn" onclick="openDrawer('hml')">Learn more</button><button class="start" onclick="openModal('hml')">Start →</button></div></div>
    <div class="ty"><div class="ic">⌂</div><h3>DSCR</h3><p>Long-term rental financing qualified on property cash flow. Build the portfolio without the paperwork circus.</p><div class="acts"><button class="learn" onclick="openDrawer('dscr')">Learn more</button><button class="start" onclick="openModal('dscr')">Start →</button></div></div>
  </div>
</div></section>

